<span id="freeTextContainer8823602755633131527">This is second M.A. Levi book I&apos;ve read, and I&apos;m lovin&apos; &apos;em!! The first book I read was &quot;Flames To The Beast&quot;. This second book is called &quot;Beast Blood Volume Two: Truer Sin&quot;. Although the second book was written first, for some reason I was lucky, and I read them in chronological order. I would recommend doing the same. <br/><br/>M. A. Levi depicts a beautiful world of fantasy and werewolves and covens and prophecies and newborn hybrids. M.A.&apos;s imagination is limitless, and this novel shows off her many t</span>
  <span id="freeText8823602755633131527" style="display:none">This is second M.A. Levi book I've read, and I'm lovin' 'em!! The first book I read was "Flames To The Beast". This second book is called "Beast Blood Volume Two: Truer Sin". Although the second book was written first, for some reason I was lucky, and I read them in chronological order. I would recommend doing the same. <br /><br />M. A. Levi depicts a beautiful world of fantasy and werewolves and covens and prophecies and newborn hybrids. M.A.'s imagination is limitless, and this novel shows off her many talents. Her writing skills deliciously create a previously unknown fantasy world and captivate my full attention. The rich detail explores M.A.'s imagination and communicates loads of interest to the reader.<br /> <br />Although this book's genre is Paranormal Fantasy, the writing is so good and so captivating, that readers of other genres will find it to be an interesting and captivating read. I'm a huge fan of M.A. Levi and I'm looking forward to reading the third book in this series. <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></span>
